Net-Syslogd version 0.09
========================

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

  perl Makefile.PL
  make
  make test
  make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Socket 1.87
  IO::Socket::IP (for IPv6 support)
  Test::Simple
  Term::ReadKey

